column41: Some of the prompts were grammatically incorrect and confused me -- such as "the conversation of the dish" which I think meant to be read "the conversion of the dish." Otherwise it was fine.
Some grammar errors made some questions cryptic
this is a pilot test from catherine

The task was somewhat unclear - I wasn't entirely sure how my relationship to the author of the fictional post was supposed to impact my response. Also, I, personally am not an avid social media user and rarely like/comment/share potentially controversial posts.
